@itszayedkhan #perfectman Meet Mr Zayed Khan, our Starbuzz of the Month! Renowned actor, producer, and style icon, Zayed shares his captivating journey of growth, self-expression, and effortless style. From iconic films like Main Hoon Na to his personal life, Zayed opens up about staying grounded, navigating fame, and embracing fatherhood. With wit and wisdom, he reveals the philosophy behind his fashion choices and the importance of setting healthy boundaries. Get ready to be inspired by Zayed’s heartfelt conversation, filled with humility, growth, and enduring curiosity. Dive into the world of a man who embodies evolution, balance, and quiet resilience.

Hello people! Witnessed a very strange yet fulfilling experience “The Butterfly Effect”🦋👐. It almost felt the universe is talking to me. The almighty has his own ways. I wish you peace and love always.😊😇 🤜🤛❤️
#nature #naturelovers #universe #blessings #gratitude #prayer

Hello people , it was my honour and pride to grace the stage for the closing show of Bombay times fashion week  yesterday for my darling friend Rohit Verma  celebraring his collection “Giddha” . It was truly nostalgic for me to come around a full circle ⭕️ in this Big beautiful world where fashion meets Bollywood . To see the pain and hard work from every individual from Tinker , tailor , choreographer, designers, technical support staff and yes show stoppers !!! A crazy machine working  in Tandem from all walks of life  backgrounds and cultures. I saw my India working with love and passion and was so proud to see all people young and old come together to nail it when crunch time has arrived . Here are a few snap shots of the BTS of hard the work that goes into the magic that is seen on stage in 30 mins . Kudos to every soul who contributed to this stunning show ! And a big shout out to all my old time peers who I met back stage 🤗😊🤜🤛❤️❤️🫵✊️🤟🎉🎉🎉🎉🙏! One more thing to my wife @malzkhan thank you for being my guardian angel ! and my sister @madhurimanigamofficial  for suggesting that I could play this part thank you ladies 🤗🤗🤗❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️🤗🤗 #fashionista #showstopper #bollywood  #bollywoodstylefile  #ethinicwear  #love  #grattitude #celebration ♠️ ❤️♠️❤️ @rohitkverma 🙏🤗🤲
